extendedInfo.description: Find the differences,   Indoor version! Play it now!This game helps improve your attention, exercise the brain, high-quality images can bring you the joy of beauty.I hope you like it.If you have any problem, please send an email to annalisa23566@gmail.com ,We will be resolved as soon as possible.How to Play:When the game starts, you will see two almost identical pictures. Note that when you press the wrong place, you will lose time.
